# Environment variables - defense-in-depth for future env-specific files
# Note: .env is currently tracked and contains only public VITE_* values (project_id, anon JWT, URL).
# These rules block future .env.production / .env.staging / .env.local etc if they appear with real secrets.
.env.*
!.env.example


